assistant: 1. Identify objects on the counter and their types.
2. Move the pot from the induction cooker to a safe location.
3. Put the boxes of "Chicky", "Rice Bubbles", and "Jello" into the dark gray cabinets.
4. Store the jars in the dark gray cabinets.
5. Place the stack of plates in the dark gray cabinets.
6. Move the gallon of water on the counter to the sink or a designated storage area.
7. Identify objects on the dining table and their types.
8. Store the box of "Shortbread" in the dark gray cabinets.
9. Put the jug on the counter or in the dark gray cabinets based on its type.
10. Place the wine glass in the dark gray cabinets or a designated glass storage.
11. Put the plate from the dining table into the stack of plates in the dark gray cabinets.
12. Move the gallon of water on the dining table to the sink or a designated storage area.
13. Wipe the counter and dining table if necessary.
14. Verify all items are stored in their designated places.
